'''1Password '''是一个由AgileBits公司开发的[[密码管理|密码管理]]软件。它能用来存放各种不同的[[密码|密码]]，除普通登录密码外，[[信用卡|信用卡]]、[[软件许可证|软件许可证]]等信息也可一同存放在经{{link-en|PBKDF2|PBKDF2}}加密<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blog.agilebits.com/2012/11/08/dont-trust-a-password-management-system-you-design-yourself/ |title=Don’t trust a password management system you design yourself! |accessdate=14 July 2014 |date=8 November 2012 |archive-date=2014-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715005136/http://blog.agilebits.com/2012/11/08/dont-trust-a-password-management-system-you-design-yourself/ }}</ref>的虚拟保险箱里，默认情况下，此加密保管库会存储在1Password的服务器上。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sspai.com/25168 |title=一个密码的另一种生活：1Password 完全评测 - 少数派 |accessdate=2016-03-06 |author=Alex周豫和 |archive-date=2016-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161122044534/http://sspai.com/25168 |dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 主密码与安全密钥 ==
当用户注册1Password时，会被要求为自己的1Password账户设置一个主密码（Master Password），当完成注册后，系统会要求用户下载一份含有自己账户的安全密钥（Secret Key）''（该密钥由系统生成）''<ref>{{Cite web|title=About your Secret Key|url=https://support.1password.com/secret-key-security/|accessdate=2020-10-11|work=1Password|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112014557/https://support.1password.com/secret-key-security/|dead-url=no}}</ref>的急救包（Emergency Kit）''（这是一份默认为.PDF格式的文件）''。在任何一台新设备上使用1Password时，都需要输入正确的1Password用户名、主密码和安全密钥才能够登录。

== 密码文件同步 ==
1Password可以在本地存放密码，不与任何远程[[服务器|服务器]]接触。也可以选择与[[Dropbox|Dropbox]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://learn2.agilebits.com/1Password4/Mac/en/Features/Sync/dropbox.html |title=Sync with Dropbox |accessdate=20 July 2014 |archive-date=2014-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140813081657/http://learn2.agilebits.com/1Password4/Mac/en/Features/Sync/dropbox.html }}</ref>（全平台），本地[[Wi-Fi|Wi-Fi]]（全平台<ref>同步至iOS必須安裝軟件</ref>），<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://learn2.agilebits.com/1Password4/Mac/en/Features/Sync/wifi.html |title=Sync using local Wi-Fi |accessdate=20 July 2014 |archive-date=2014-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141210011751/https://learn2.agilebits.com/1Password4/Mac/en/Features/Sync/wifi.html }}</ref>或[[iCloud|iCloud]]（仅Mac与iOS设备）同步。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303647204579545801399272852 |title=The Best Way to Manage All Your Passwords |last=Fowler |first=Geoffrey |work=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]] |accessdate=14 July 2014 |archive-date=2014-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022140746/http://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303647204579545801399272852 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/04/technology/personaltech/04smart.html |title=Managing Your Passwords, With a Little Help From an App |last=Tedeschi |first=Bob |date=3 November 2010 |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |accessdate=14 July 2014 |archive-date=2020-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200617182254/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/04/technology/personaltech/04smart.html }}</ref>。同时也可以选择通过订阅付费使用由1Password.com提供的的数据同步服务，数据将加密存储于远程服务器中。

== 浏览器扩展程序 ==
1Password浏览器扩展程序可用在[[Microsoft_Edge|Edge]]、[[Firefox|Firefox]]、[[Chrome|Chrome]]、[[Safari|Safari]]、[[Brave浏览器|Brave]]等主流网络浏览器上<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://agilebits.com/onepassword/extensions |title=1Password Browser Extensions |accessdate=15 Feb 2016 |archive-date=2018-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180323220440/https://agilebits.com/onepassword/extensions }}</ref>，实现自动填充，提示记住新密码等功能。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://guides.agilebits.com/1password-windows/4/en/topic/the-browser-extensions |title=The browser extensions |accessdate=15 Feb 2016 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306040746/https://guides.agilebits.com/1password-windows/4/en/topic/the-browser-extensions }}</ref>

== 公司历史 ==

2019 年 11 月 14 日，1Password 宣布与风险投资公司 Accel 建立合作伙伴关系，后者在 A 轮融资中投资了 2 亿美元，并获得了该公司的少数股权。这是 1Password 历史上的第一笔外部融资，也是 Accel 迄今为止最大的单笔投资。<ref name="mg21">{{Cite web|url=https://www.mg21.com/1password.html|title=加拿大全平台密码管理软件开发商：AgileBits Inc. (1Password)|publisher=美股之家|date=2021-07-30|access-date=2021-07-31|archive-date=2021-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210731023119/https://www.mg21.com/1password.html}}</ref>

2021 年，1Password 收购了荷兰网络安全公司 SecretHub。它还以 20 亿美元的估值筹集了 1 亿美元的B轮融资。<ref name="mg21"/>

